        <h3>References and further reading</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Klobuchar, J. A. (1987). Ionospheric time-delay algorithm for single-frequency GPS users. <em>IEEE Transactions on Aerospace and Electronic Systems</em>, 23(3), 325–331.</li>
          <li>Nava, B., Coïsson, P. & Radicella, S. M. (2008). A new version of the NeQuick ionosphere electron density model. <em>Journal of Atmospheric and Solar-Terrestrial Physics</em>, 70(15), 1856–1862.</li>
          <li>Galileo OS SIS ICD — NeQuick-G ionospheric model specification. <a href="https://www.gsc-europa.eu" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GSC Europa →</a></li>
          <li>Hofmann-Wellenhof, B., Lichtenegger, H. & Wasle, E. (2008). <em>GNSS — Global Navigation Satellite Systems</em>. Springer. Chapter 5.</li>
          <li>Teunissen, P. J. G. & Montenbruck, O. (eds.) (2017). <em>Springer Handbook of Global Navigation Satellite Systems</em>. Chapter 19.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

